messages.messageBody:
No, not much. Long shoes help so that there is room in
the toe box to place the extra sock when you have to
pull it down off of the toes.

I think the socks are worse than they used to be.
Men's socks seem :-) to be a little better than
women's. Kids are the worst. I get good socks my
size and in boy colors and shrink them for Roy, as
they don't come (that I have found) in his in the
middle size.

Sharon of the Swamp
